		const FAQ = array(
			'What is NFT marketplace?'           => 'NFT Marketplace for WordPress by miniOrange is a plugin that converts your WooCommerce store into an NFT Marketplace. It supports features like minting NFTs, listing NFTs and selling NFTs. All this is done on the versatile Polygon blockchain. NFT Marketplace brings the world of NFTs to your doorstep with the ease of accessibility of a WooCommerce store.',
			'How to import NFTs?'                => 'In order to import NFTs, simply enter the collection address in the Import NFTs section of the miniOrange NFT Marketplace menu, and click on create a store. This will automatically publish your NFTs in the products section of WooCommerce.',
			'How to mint NFTs?'                  => 'Mint NFTs by first creating a product on WooCommerce. While creating the product, check the NFT Product check-box option in the product menu. Then, head over to the miniOrange NFT Marketplace menu. Here you will be able to see your product. Click on the Mint NFT button next to your product and sign the transaction requests to mint your NFT.',
